Sock sneakers are one of the coolest trends that have hit 2018. Just as when you think clothes couldn't get any cooler, we're hit with a bomb. We've had sock heels and now have sock sneakers. Sock sneakers are sneakers made with a thick sock material. When worn, these sneakers hug the foot and ankle depending on how high/long the 'sock' is. These sneakers are quite popular in black but there are other colours surfacing. They also are popular in an ankle high top sneaker. Both men are women can rock these sneakers. You can pair these sneakers with a trendy tracksuit or a figure hugging dress. See pictures below of sock sneakers: I want a pair but they odeee expensive???? follow @lil.barbzz for more????‍?? - - - - - #shoes #sneakers #balenciaga #balenciagasneakers #socksneakers #baddie #baddies #explore #explorepage #postpage A post shared by  barbzz?? (@lil.barbzz) on Aug 10, 2018 at 7:20pm PDT    Second Time Around ?? The Sick Kicks Are Restocked ?? #RichBoysClub #ShopRichBoys #BackInStock #TapToShop A post shared by  Official Rich Boys Brand, Inc. (@rich_boys) on Nov 3, 2018 at 1:20pm PDT    For the 2nd capsule collection for Closed, Girbaud manages once again to break up boundaries in fashion and to create new worlds. This trendy sock sneakers for men, made of compact and elastic quality with woven circles, are part of his edition. @closedxgirbaud @girbaud_official @closedofficial.men #girbaud #sneakers #socksneakers #closedofficial A post shared by  Closed Official (@closedofficial) on Sep 3, 2018 at 9:10am PDT    25-31 - 295€ #balenciagakids #socksneakers #trendyshoes #christmasshopping #worldwideshipping #????????????????????? A post shared by  ???????????? (@lux_trend_kids) on Nov 6, 2018 at 1:02am PST    O tênis meia ou Sock Sneacker é uma tendencia mundial, unindo conforto e beleza ele veio para deixar seus looks ainda mais estilosos! ??????Que tal?! R$ 379,90/5 x 75,98 @carranooficial #socksneakers #tênis #moda #tendência #conforto #newcollection #carrano #